short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Extension to Automute tabs and keep only the focused one playing sound

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
A simple extension to Automute tabs and keep only the focused one playing sound.

This extension is designed for people who keeps multiple sound playing tabs and want to hear only the focused one. The extension will mute all secondary tabs that tries to play any sound.
If you switch to another tab, the new one will be the one you'll hear.

Bugs or feature requests should be reported at https://github.com/matheusvellone/automuter/issues

Source code can be found at: https://github.com/matheusvellone/automuter
